# This file ensures the _drafts/ directory is tracked by git even when empty.
#
# Drafts go here as plain markdown files. They are committed to the repo but
# excluded from the Zola build via the build configuration.
#
# Why this exists: consistent with public-from-day-one — half-formed thinking
# is visible in `git log` if anyone looks, but doesn't appear on the site
# until intentionally moved to content/.
